[I am certain that the Pasteur Institute, Cayenne, would be interested in
these specimens and would either have knowledgeable individuals available or
be able to point Jean-Christophe in the right direction. If anyone else is
interested in assisting, please contact him directly. Sounds like a good
opportunity for an arbovirus (or hantavirus/arenavirus) serosurvey in French
Guiana, a fascinating place. -- Mod CHC]
